Sentencas: A new system, (La(0.8)Sr(0.2))(1-x)Ag(x)MnO(3+delta)(LSAM, x <= 0.2), is developed as current collector for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: LSAM is prepared by a modified sal gel method and presents a single phase.
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The shrinkage temperature reduces from 1150 degrees C to 800 degrees C with an addition of 15 mol% Ag to La(0.8)Sr(0.2)MnO(3+delta) (LSM20).
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The contact resistance between the current collector and the cathode is measured, and the influence of Ag content on the contact resistance is investigated.
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The result shows that the contact resistance using (La(0.8)Sr(0.2))(0.85)Ag(0.15)MnO(3+delta) (LSAM15) as current collector is about 12 m Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C, which is close to the value using expensive Pt paste as current collector.
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This new system is a promising current collecting material for the practical application of SOFC.
Titulo: Easy sintering of silver doped lanthanum strontium manganite current collector for solid oxide fuel cells
